_sText:
Yes, as my laptop is to a repair, I can't work on de_allanbanallah. 
So i came up with this map.. ka_Dont-Fall, and ka_Dont-Fall_orange

I included 2 styles of texture versions on this map, a black/grey and a orange/black version. The sun is also different between the 2 maps. The sunlight is more orange in ka_Dont-Fall_orange than in the other.

Credits:
Creation: TwixyTwix
Idea: TwixyTwix
Textures: Valve

I will recommend you to put your server on sv_gravity 300-400 and sv_friction 2. That makes the map 100 times more fun! :D

If you have any ideas/suggestions, they are welcome :D
